<bioghist encodinganalog="545">
<p>Edwin J. Johnson was editor and publisher of the Ironwood Daily Globe.</p>
</bioghist>



<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>The collection consists of photographs and slides relating to Ironwood and surrounding area. These images include street views, parades, lumbering and mining activities, local events and disasters, building projects, and miscellaneous. The collection also includes newspaper clippings of his editorials and other articles relating to his newspaper career and civic interests.</p>
</scopecontent>

